popInstructions1.message: To automatically connect the extension to your installation of Team Password Manager, open a new tab on your browser and navigate to Team Password Manager.

popInstructions2.message: Log in if you're logged out. If you're already logged in just refresh the current page. When the extension icon turns blue, the extension is connected.
